{"tid":50833,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一份無送到出去既禮物","createTime":"2016-12-22T17:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T08:28:48.000Z","uid":48918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23861d9d5c0a5867b3e82e22b49d5829bb740606","tid":50833,"uid":48918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"上年聖誕係logon買既3d拉花機<br />\n當時諗住送比曖晦對象 因為佢鐘意飲咖啡<br />\n但最後因為種種原因冇送到 <br />\n宜家已經同佢冇聯絡 <br />\n份禮物仲原封不動係放左我個櫃到成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b46e00ef14fb6e0cb81287dd96dfdbcee6071c9","tid":50833,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5232ca57b39f3769cadb5c8607d621affa06f4d0","tid":50833,"uid":8864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"一隻求婚介指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8406962e713ce9c11dcfe6ba4aaaf14996afbb6","tid":50833,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3de145debd523b27bad768b9d7e76a6d25b8b3a","tid":50833,"uid":45985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a36aa47720f30dfe961265aa96aa48358a1ab1","tid":50833,"uid":47428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7afe4af0e34993859fea36bbdf98caf9946c906","tid":50833,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我珍而重之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送唔出"},{"pid":"c578af01a3e5e89c4f6be35ea4cc88a6b4d1816c","tid":50833,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"刻左我同佢生日既一對鑰匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6abc596a43daaae1a5986dc52912202b35278b2","tid":50833,"uid":56836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"明信片，旅行買的，上面有兩隻企鵝互相依偎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未送得出已經分了手"},{"pid":"36358038d8b78c045fa6ca2f335593d07b78786f","tid":50833,"uid":36530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"個年經過muji佢話架模型車好靚 之後偷偷地買左返屋企砌再去宜家傢私買左個燈模 放架車係內面<br />\n整得好有心思但最後佢拒絕我送俾佢 送唔岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後on99放左係床頭 第三年見到頂唔順一手掉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a66abebcf37d89609effbcd555bd56034f3632","tid":50833,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"一瓶朱古力 <br />\n佢好鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買曬好多種唔同款嘅放係個一玻璃瓶到<br />\n第二日佢係ig post 相話識左個新男友"},{"pid":"4e38d652b3da723796f7237a63419694c213612a","tid":50833,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T20:47:05.000Z","msg":"聖誕節禮物<br />\n一個盒擺左本簿 入面寫好左我plan好晒去旅行既行程 曬左啲相痴落去想比佢揀住咩地方 畫左啲公仔 <br />\n因為個排好忙好少見佢所以想送個旅行比佢 結果聖誕都未到就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16807dab6d855758cc7c92abde2c3a51d8e5fcc3","tid":50833,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:02:16.000Z","msg":"訂左野畀曖昧對象 準備做聖誕禮物<br />\n一個手作既盆栽 訂左一對<br />\n係台灣手作店整既 果陣間店話趕唔切整畀我<br />\n之後我打左一大段野畀店主<br />\n話我過左聖誕就離開香港半年 想係聖誕同個男仔表白<br />\n之後送盆野畀佢 想佢係我唔係香港嗰陣好好照顧佢<br />\n等我返香港<br />\n間店收到個message話好感動 即刻打尖整左我張單先<br />\n<br />\n最後我收到份禮物嗰陣 同個男仔已經冇咩點聯絡 聖誕仲放左我飛機 佢一月仲同另一個我識既女仔拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1cfce633f3fe6fe746467bddbb4d08ce05fd03","tid":50833,"uid":27609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:33:34.000Z","msg":"畢業公仔 戒指"},{"pid":"4c92ee600222ae5a1d4657e7a1b5c207d72dacce","tid":50833,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:34:30.000Z","msg":"自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e22d51dadd568f343b052255deb62a53b5dc25","tid":50833,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:47:35.000Z","msg":"佢話呢個聖誕想收自制禮物<br />\n我做左少少野手工野諗住24號送比佢<br />\n約佢佢話唔出 chok多幾下手都分撚埋<br />\n件禮物應該係堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b95005b14690c444b9ac67756ec2f09980b469","tid":50833,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:51:17.000Z","msg":"自己 同大家既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e4641bb8048b3d4a111d00c688e1c753068234","tid":50833,"uid":50956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:56:05.000Z","msg":"以前學完日文 寫左封感謝信比個老師 如果到而家仲未送出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3160d720ae054f91e6b7a5004f0f91273be09199","tid":50833,"uid":61917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T21:57:12.000Z","msg":"耳機<br />\n不過後來嘈左交 就無送出去 <br />\n變左自己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84dbb1602756d2a13cd9efe3ae54f3484619868e","tid":50833,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明信片，旅行買的，上面有兩隻企鵝互相依偎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未送得出已經分了手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/asse